{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Film Live-Action Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun Siap Membawamu Kembali ke Masa Remaja","content":"<p>Kalian ada yang udah nonton anime atau baca manga Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun? Ayo baca manganya dan nonton serial animenya, karena Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun akan diadaptasi dalam bentuk film <em>Live Action</em> dan tayang tahun 2018 ini!</p>\n<p>Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun berkisah tentang hubungan antara remaja bernama Shizuku Mizutani dan Haru Yoshida. Shizuku, sebagaimana pelajar Jepang lainnya, lebih mengutamakan belajar dan rencana masa depannya, sedangkan Haru jarang sekali datang ke sekolah.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44669\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44669\" data-attachment-id=\"44669\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/attachment/01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44669\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang.jpg\" alt=\"01 tonari no kaibutsu-kun\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-mang-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44669\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Manga Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun, bukan BDSM, lho! (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Ketika Shizuku mendapat tugas untuk mengantarkan <em>print-out</em> kelas ke rumah Haru, hubungan mereka sebagai teman pun dimulai. Shizuku, yang awalnya dikenal sebagai wanita yang dingin, tersentuh kepada kepolosan Haru akan pengetahuan minimnya tentang hubungan antar manusia. Walaupun dikenal sebagai monster kasar dan sulit dijinakkan, Haru sebenarnya orang yang baik.</p>\n<p>Haru dengan cepat menyatakan cintanya kepada Shizuku, tetapi tak semudah itu bagi Shizuku. Meski dia wanita yang pintar, Shizuku membutuhkan waktu yang lama untuk menyadari dan menerima perasaannya terhadap Haru. Karena mereka sama-sama antisosial, mereka saling membantu satu sama lain dalam hal hubungan pertemanan maupun di keluarga masing-masing.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44670\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44670\" data-attachment-id=\"44670\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/attachment/02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44670\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime.jpg\" alt=\"02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-anime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44670\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anime Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun. (Sumber: MyAnimeList)</p></div>\n<p>Manga yang ditulis oleh Robico ini pernah mendapat serialisasi di majalah <em>Dessert</em> terbitan Kondansha pada 2008 hingga 2014. Karena kepopulerannya, manga ini mendapat adaptasi anime yang tayang pada akhir 2012 lalu. Adaptasi <em>Live-Action</em> pun dibuat dan akan diluncurkan di Jepang pada 27 April 2018 ini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44671\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44671\" data-attachment-id=\"44671\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/attachment/03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44671\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film.jpg\" alt=\"03 tonari no kaibutsu-kun film\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-film-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44671\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Live-Action Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun. (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Kualitas film ini pun tak perlu diragukan kalau dilihat dari deretan artis yang mengisi peran. Masaki Suda, yang menapaki karir lewat Kamen Rider W, mendapat peran sebagai Haru Yoshida, setelah sebelumnya memerankan Shinpachi Shimura di <em>Live-Action</em> Gintama dan Karuma Akabane di <em>Live-Action Assassination Classroom.</em></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44672\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44672\" data-attachment-id=\"44672\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/attachment/04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44672\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru.jpg\" alt=\"04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-haru-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44672\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Masaki Suda sebagai Haru Yoshida. Cocok nggak? (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Untuk lawan main dari Masaki Suda pun tak kalah populer. Pemeran Shizuku Mizutani jatuh kepada Tao Tsuchiya, yang sukses berperan sebagai Naho Takamiya di <em>Live-Action Orang</em>e pada 2015 lalu dan membawanya merebut penghargaan sebagai <em>Rookie of the Year</em>. Kemampuan aktingnya di film bergenre drama tak perlu diragukan lagi.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44673\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44673\" data-attachment-id=\"44673\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/attachment/05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44673\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku.jpg\" alt=\"05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-shizuku-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44673\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tao Tsuchiya sebagai Shizuku Mizutani. Kawaii!!! (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Untuk aktor dan aktris pendukung, ada Yuki Furukawa yang berperan sebagai kakak dari Haru. Ada pula Yuki Yamada yang menjadi pesaing cinta Haru dalam merebut hati Shizuku. Tidak lupa ada Elaiza Ikeda, Minami Hamabe, Shiru Sano, Mokomichi Hayami, dan Gaku Sano. Mereka semua adalah pemain yang sudah berpengalaman membintangi drama ataupun film <em>Live-Action</em>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44674\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44674\" data-attachment-id=\"44674\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/attachment/06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44674\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast.jpg\" alt=\"06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-cast-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44674\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pemeran utama dan pendukung. Gimana? (Sumber: natalie.mu)</p></div>\n<p>Masih butuh alasan lagi untuk nonton? Penyanyi papan atas Jepang, Kana Nishino, mengisi <em>soundtrack</em> di film ini. Mau dengar lagunya? Coba simak trailer dari <em>Live-Action</em> Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun berikut ini:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gAXZVDc2mXo\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Masih kurang? Ada satu lagi nih:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/l7o8J-lU2ZI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Dari kedua <em>trailer</em> itu, bisa dilihat kalau film bergenre <em>romance comedy</em> ini bakalan bikin kalian <em>baper</em>. Kalau masih berpikir cinta monyet remaja itu sebenarnya sederhana, kita akan disajikan dengan cinta yang lebih rumit dan penuh dengan perselisihan karena kedua karakter yang nggak mau mengalah.</p>\n<p>Ada pula adegan yang bikin penonton bisa <em>doki-doki</em> dan <em>cengar-cengir</em> sendirian (bagi yang nontonnya sendiria,  ya). Kalau kalian pernah merasakan pahit-manisnya romansa masa remaja, film ini bisa membantu untuk <em>flashback</em> lagi ke masa-masa itu.</p>\n<p>Nah, karena film ini juga baru akan tayang di Jepang, belum ada kepastian kapan film ini akan dibawa ke Indonesia. Apakah kalian setuju kalau film ini layak ditayangkan di bioskop-bioskop Indonesia? Kalau setuju, sebarkan artikel ini supaya bisa mengundang ketertarikan dari promotor film dan membawanya ke Indonesia, ya!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44675\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44675\" data-attachment-id=\"44675\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-live-action-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun/attachment/07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44675\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru.jpg\" alt=\"07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/07-tonari-no-kaibutsu-kun-chizuru-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44675\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Minami Hamabe + kacamata jadi makin kawaii, ya! (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Kalian yang suka dengan cowok tampan dan cewek cantik, pasti juga bakal setuju kalau film ini layak ditonton, apalagi setelah melihat deretan selebriti yang berperan. Wajah manis Tao Tsuchiya sih tetap jadi daya tarik penulis buat nonton film ini. Ada juga Minami Hamabe, yang pernah berperan di Live-Action Ajin dan Elaiza Ikeda yang menjadi peran utama di film Minna! Esper Dayo. Kalian suka siapa di film ini? Jangan lupa beri komentar di bawah ini ya…</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"a193f7fa-24fb-5439-9139-bfbbd28d6bf2"}}}